  "comment_text": {
    "sn1.48:1.1": "These verses are also found at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn2.20/en/sujato'>SN 2.20</a>, where they are attributed to Anāthapiṇḍika. ",
    "sn1.48:4.1": "Anāthapiṇḍika was especially devoted to Sāriputta (see <a href='https://suttacentral.net/mn143/en/sujato'>MN 143</a>). "
  },
